veloped to integrate kinetic data obtained from different experimental constructs and/or from molecular dynamics simulations of a biomolecule of interest. The hFRET source code, graphical user interface, and user manual can be downloaded as freeware at https://github.com/GonzalezBiophysicsLab/hFRET.},
